query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('admob',
'awt',
'console-application',
'count',
'directory',
'file-io',
'focus',
'grails',
'logging',
'phantomjs',
'python-requests',
'slice',
'spring-data');
